$interpreted: Nigel: Hyacinthus, please! We're almost there!
Nigel: BACK FIENDS! I don't have time for you!
Naya: Let me help, we can move faster.
Nigel: Good lord, where are these monsters coming from?!
Naya: Grab Hyacinthus, let's slash our way out!
Naya: We can put her here for now, bring the others in!
Angelia: Let me wipe the sweat off Hyacinthus...
Naya: Pinned her down, but what do we do next?!
Angelia: Naya, tie her up. After the worst is over, we'll take Hyacinthus to a doctor.
Naya: It's no use. There's no coming back from the dead!
Angelia: How do you know? There's still hope for us!
Lio: She's right, Cin is still alive! "Ohana" means family. Family means nobody gets left behind!
Nigel: ...Not at all. You even protected the children, you did very well...
Hyacinthus: Great...I couldn't be of help before...could only watch you...take on everything yourself...
Nigel: Hush. Close your eyes and rest a bit.
Hyacinthus: ...*cough*...after I sleep, will I still be able...to see everyone's faces...?
Nigel: Yes. Eve will be here, so will I. Just like old times.
Hyacinthus: Wonderful...*cough*...back to the good ol' days...
